[The complete situation report is available at http://newsletters.afro.who.int/outbreak-dashboards/8958jw9jjpo1it646w1k05?a=6&p=53722888&t=29558418.

The noted continuous efflux of refugees is very concerning since some may become infected and will inadvertently move the virus. It is critical that the bordering countries maintain extremely high vigilance for cases. - Mod.LK

